<item>
            <title>[FLINK-19750] Deserializer is not opened in Kafka consumer when restoring from state</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-19750</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When a job using Kafka consumer is recovered from a checkpoint or savepoint, the&#160;&lt;tt&gt;open&lt;/tt&gt;&#160;method of the record deserializer is not called. This is possibly because&#160;&lt;tt&gt;this.deserializer.open&lt;/tt&gt;&#160;is put into the else clause by mistake, which will only be called if the job has a clean start.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
